(208, 88, 'description', 'UglyFacez is a site I made devoted to promoting healthy habits among children. It is made to accompany a short children''s story by Neil Shulman called The Great Face-off! In the story, kids are tired of their parents smoking and polluting their young lungs with second-hand smoke, so they decide to make ugly faces and hold them until all the parents of the world finally give in and agree to stop smoking. On the web site, kids can log in and upload pictures of themselves making crazy faces and vote for who makes the best crazy face! The site exhibits knowledge of PHP, Javascript, and SQL, as well as building web applications.'),
