(2287, 613, 'description', 'The redesign of El Jimador''s web site was taken on by <a target="_blank" href="http://www.engauge.com">Engauge</a> in early 2013. The site, built in Drupal and fully responsive among all devices and browsers, is a robust example of a corporate-level site that uses branding and imagery to drive the site''s appeal. The structure of the site itself is very interesting in its layout and unique segmentation&mdash;not only purely for its form factor, but also for the process of its implementation. It''s a great example of both a multilingual and multi-country site. I took on the project for its second round of development and led the development cycle from there to its completion and launch. ¡Olé! Tequila shots all around! All branding and content of the site is property of <a style="text-decoration: underline;" target="_blank" href="http://www.brown-forman.com/">Brown-Forman</a>, and all design and development of the site is copyright <a style="text-decoration: underline;" target="_blank" href="http://www.engauge.com">Engauge</a>.'),
