(2339, 632, 'description', 'Internet security is an extremely important concept in computing today. You''ve heard the horror stories&mdash;Apple''s prototypes leaked to the public, Target''s databases scoured for credit card information, identity theft occurring daily all over the world, and more. That''s why Cisco put together this interactive experience to educate business owner''s on the importance of security, some of the common pitfall''s people run into, and how goals and perspective differ between business decision makers and technical decision makers. All content copyright <a style="text-decoration: underline;" href="http://cisco.com">Cisco</a>.'),
