(2363, 647, 'description', 'Verizon is Moxie''s biggest client, and for 2014, I was a part of the team that was in charge of rebuilding and refactoring their site (specifically <a href="http://www.verizonwireless.com">www.verizonwireless.com</a>)for Verizon Wireless&mdash;their cell phone and wireless services sector. Since this project is a much longer term and ongoing project, it creates a different workflow that many developers are not used to&mdash;from always referencing branding and style guidelines, to getting previously built pages, widgets, and code working and interacting with new builds, to working with a huge team, to keeping up with all of the code standards that all code must strictly follow in order to be approved. Though among all these challenges, working on something that is known and being used by so many people around the world is definitely cool. Moxie''s work with the Verizon site will continue over the next few years, but here are a few sections that I have helped work on so far. Please note that all work portrayed here is ultimately property of Moxie Interactive and Verizon.'),
