(615, 1, '2013-11-14 19:44:26', '2013-11-14 19:44:26', 'A web site is a powerful tool. It allows companies to divert resources from customer services, users to reference information freely at their own \r\nleisure, brands to direct attention to their social media channels, retailers to offer services that they previously could not, and organizations \r\nto spread information more effectively than they ever could without a web presence. There are certainly hundreds of other advantages to invest in\r\nweb services and mobile applications than I could ever even take the time to list out, but the reasoning is all the same: having a web site is not\r\na choice for a successful business in the 21st century&mdash;it is a requirement.', 'Web Development', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '64-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-14 19:44:26', '2013-11-14 19:44:26', '', 64, 'http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/64-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
