(63, 1, '2012-12-03 15:16:59', '2012-12-03 15:16:59', 'Whether Graphic Design, procedural interactions, film, illustration, or other visually-driven forms of media, visual media is the most prominent art form in our culture. The topic is so broad, it''s difficult to generalize it into a single category. Here are a few pieces that focus on Graphic Design and static visual media in general.', 'Visual Design', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'visual-design', '', '', '2012-12-03 23:52:25', '2012-12-03 23:52:25', '', 12, 'http://jrstrauss.net/portfolio-new/?page_id=63', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(64, 1, '2012-12-03 17:14:48', '2012-12-03 17:14:48', 'A web site is a powerful tool. It allows companies to divert resources from customer services, users to reference information freely at their own leisure, brands to direct attention to their social media channels, retailers to offer services that they previously could not, and organizations to spread information more effectively than they ever could without a web presence. There are certainly hundreds of other advantages to invest in web services and mobile applications than I could ever even take the time to list out, but the reasoning is all the same: having a web site is not a choice for a successful business in the 21st century&mdash;it is a requirement.', 'Web Development', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'web-development', '', '', '2013-11-14 19:45:11', '2013-11-14 19:45:11', '', 12, 'http://jrstrauss.net/portfolio-new/?page_id=64', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(65, 1, '2012-12-03 17:15:18', '2012-12-03 17:15:18', 'Fall 2010: Computer Graphics is a class in which students explore the ways to create realistic models on-screen and create procedurally generated and developed graphics. All models are created purely by text. Some of the topics covered include: rendering in 3D, accurate physics modeling, advanced and dynamic geometry, working with curves, and matrix operations and transformation, just to name a few. You will need Java installed to view any of them.', 'Computer Graphics', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'computer-graphics', '', '', '2012-12-04 06:15:09', '2012-12-04 06:15:09', '', 12, 'http://jrstrauss.net/portfolio-new/?page_id=65', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(66, 1, '2012-12-03 17:15:37', '2012-12-03 17:15:37', '<h2>Ellis Island</h2>\r\nFall 2010: Ellis Island is a research project started and currently in development at Georgia Tech as an experimental game design collaboration. The game is a massively multiplayer online game that facilitates online narrative play. The project has been run by various students over the last few years, and for one year, I helped develop 3D models in Maya to populate objects in the game. The game is set in New York City in the 1920''s. Take a look at the project profile on Georgia Tech website <a href="http://www.lcc.gatech.edu/school/featuredprojects.php?id=11">here.</a>', '3D Modeling', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3d-modeling', '', '', '2012-12-04 06:18:35', '2012-12-04 06:18:35', '', 12, 'http://jrstrauss.net/portfolio-new/?page_id=66', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(67, 1, '2012-12-03 17:16:02', '2012-12-03 17:16:02', 'I don''t consider myself a photographer. I''m not pursuing any sort of photography related job. Nonetheless, working in any branch of media, it''s a good skill to have at least some sort of expertise in. You should have a trained eye for framing, composition, negative space, color, lighting, exposure, and depth of field, to name a few. So even though I don''t specialize in photography, these skills relate very closely with Web Design, Graphic Design, and other visual media. I mainly take pictures just for the fun of it.', 'Photography', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'photography', '', '', '2012-12-12 04:29:00', '2012-12-12 04:29:00', '', 12, 'http://jrstrauss.net/portfolio-new/?page_id=67', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(68, 1, '2012-12-03 17:16:27', '2012-12-03 17:16:27', 'I don''t have a great hand for drawing, but I do like to take sketches that I think are cool and digitize them in my own time for fun. There''s something about completely inked and colored drawings that I think makes them look great.', 'Illustration', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'illustration', '', '', '2012-12-04 06:20:03', '2012-12-04 06:20:03', '', 12, 'http://jrstrauss.net/portfolio-new/?page_id=68', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(69, 1, '2012-12-03 17:16:49', '2012-12-03 17:16:49', 'If I''ve learned anything about animation over the years it''s this: animating anything is extremely difficult!', 'Animation', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'animation', '', '', '2012-12-04 06:20:28', '2012-12-04 06:20:28', '', 12, 'http://jrstrauss.net/portfolio-new/?page_id=69', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(70, 1, '2012-12-03 17:17:04', '2012-12-03 17:17:04', 'Whether Graphic Design, procedural interactions, film, illustration, or other visually-driven forms of media, visual media is the most prominent art form in our culture. The topic is so broad, it''s difficult to generalize it into a single category. Here are a few pieces that focus on Graphic Design and static visual media in general.', 'Game Design', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'game-design', '', '', '2012-12-14 07:18:27', '2012-12-14 07:18:27', '', 12, 'http://jrstrauss.net/portfolio-new/?page_id=70', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(71, 1, '2012-12-03 17:17:17', '2012-12-03 17:17:17', 'Back in the day (you know, the age of grandpas and dinosaurs), people did all mathematical calculations using only pen and paper. Sure, maybe they had tools like simple calculators and protractors, but certainly nothing that even comes close to the power of technology in present-day. Computing has completely changed the face of mathematics. What used to take hours to calculate and was extremely prone to error on the many steps towards the solution can now be calculated in nanoseconds. But in order to get to this point (enter trusty programmer), someone had to procedurally define these functions and algorithms. Here are a few examples of functions and mathematical processes in the field of Calculus and Linear Algebra that I translated from paper to terminal.', 'Computational Calculus', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'computational-calculus', '', '', '2013-02-11 20:02:15', '2013-02-11 20:02:15', '', 12, 'http://jrstrauss.net/portfolio-new/?page_id=71', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(72, 1, '2012-12-03 23:09:27', '2012-12-03 23:09:27', 'Problem statement:\r\n\r\n<em>For this first project, create a poster that reflects your most important fears and/or desires. To generate ideas for the project, ask yourself: What makes me nervous? What causes me to worry? What excites me? What draws my attention? What do I need and want? Also look for inspiration in the long tradition of political, cultural and commercial posters. You''ll be creating several versions of your poster, so select a topic that will sustain your interest over time. Create three mock-ups of your poster as a way to explore a range of visual communication strategies.</em>\r\n\r\n<em>Your poster should include both graphical and typographical elements. For this first version, use a limited palette of black, white and gray; for the final poster (Version 2.0) you can explore a broader range of color options. Scale is important, make your finished poster at least</em> 16''''x16'''';<em> explore a range of sizes as you determine your final composition. Incorporate key elements of visual design; skillfully create mark, line, texture, and shape. Be conscious of your typographic decisions; consider the letterforms, spacing and format of text. And develop a compositional strategy that foregrounds your message.</em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nFor the final turn-in, I turned in a greyscale version of this image since it was required for the assignment, but personally, I am more fond of the colored version. Since the poster was supposed to display our most important hopes and desires, I tried to communicate the idea that sometimes the people in our lives who are the most important to us and the most dear to us are those that hurt us the most. This idea represents a very stark contrast of emotions and therefore I had to be careful as to balance those emotions equally.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/poster1.png" rel="shadowbox"><img class="center three-quarters wp-image-76" style="margin-top: 100px;" title="Personal Poster 1.0" src="http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/poster1.png" alt="" /></a>\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Personal Poster 1.0', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'personal-poster-1', '', '', '2012-12-04 02:07:11', '2012-12-04 02:07:11', '', 0, 'http://jrstrauss.net/portfolio-new/?post_type=portfolio-piece&#038;p=72', 10, 'portfolio-piece', '', 0),
