(126, 1, '2012-12-12 07:40:04', '2012-12-12 07:40:04', '<div>This was a card my friend Jacob Bennett made for my brother when he graduated high school a few years ago. I thought it was a hilarious picture and a really cool drawing, so I decided to fully illustrate it. Jacob did the entire original sketch.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n\n<hr />\n\n</div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href="http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/graduation.png"><img class="center size-full wp-image-358" alt="graduation" src="http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/graduation.png" width="799" height="600" /></a></div>', 'Graduation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '124-autosave', '', '', '2012-12-12 07:40:04', '2012-12-12 07:40:04', '', 124, 'http://jrstrauss.net/portfolio-new/124-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(127, 1, '2013-04-30 02:42:57', '2013-04-30 02:42:57', 'For my senior project, I made a web site that kids can log on to and post pictures of them making crazy faces. They can rate the pictures that other kids post and decide who makes the best faces. The site will display winners each month saying, "This is what your face will look like if you start smoking," to try and encourage kids to refrain from picking up smoking. The idea was presented by Doctor Neil Shulman from Emory University, taken from a short children''s story he wrote. I took pictures from the book, originally xeroxed and stapled together in black and white and illustrated them to decorate the site with.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href="http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/uglyfacez-illustration-1.png"><img class="center illustration size-full wp-image-129" style="margin-bottom: 200px; padding-top: 20px;" title="Uglyfacez Illustration" src="http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/uglyfacez-illustration-1.png" alt="" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/uglyfacez-illustration-2.png"><img class="center illustration size-full wp-image-128" title="Uglyfacez Illustration" style="pasrc="http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/uglyfacez-illustration-2.png" alt="" /></a>', 'Uglyfacez', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '122-autosave', '', '', '2013-04-30 02:42:57', '2013-04-30 02:42:57', '', 122, 'http://jrstrauss.net/portfolio-new/122-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
