(538, 1, '2013-02-12 18:13:19', '2013-02-12 18:13:19', '<p>Since Blog OnAir is a site that emphasizes clean methods of transportation, it''s important that its users be able to participate in the Blog OnAir activities while mobile. Why should the user wait until he gets home to log his public transportation when he can do so while he rides the bus? Adolescents are very often using mobile devices and moving around, therefore it''s important that the Blog OnAir site facilitate this and thus, the Blog OnAir mobile site was born.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can view the live site by navigating any mobile device to <a href="http://blogonair.org">http://blogonair.org</a></p>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/BlogOnAirScreen1.png"><img style="float: left; max-width: 49%;" alt="BlogOnAirScreen1" src="http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/BlogOnAirScreen1.png" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/BlogOnAirScreen2.png"><img style="float: right; max-width: 49%;" alt="BlogOnAirScreen2" src="http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/BlogOnAirScreen2.png" /></a>\r\n<div style="clear: both; margin-top: 20px;"></div>\r\n<a href="http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/BlogOnAirScreen3.png"><img style="max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: auto auto;" alt="BlogOnAirScreen3" src="http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/BlogOnAirScreen3.png" /></a>\r\n<div style="clear: both; margin-top: 20px;"></div>\r\n<a href="http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/BlogOnAirScreen4.png"><img style="float: left; max-width: 49%;" alt="BlogOnAirScreen4" src="http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/BlogOnAirScreen4.png" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/BlogOnAirScreen5.png"><img style="float: right; max-width: 49%;" alt="BlogOnAirScreen5" src="http://portfolio.jrstrauss.ne